children.value: What is The Smart Pantry app?
Powered by hardware and software, The Smart Pantry app allows users to track food items stored in their kitchen pantry.
What is the Smart Pantry mission?
Aid elders in remembering their food items and living more independently​.
Reduce food waste and malnutrition among elders.
What does The Smart Pantry app do?
Allows a user to create a pantry and track food items stored in their pantry
Allows a user to add an item to the pantry by scanning its barcode or manually adding the information
Allows a user to remove an item from the pantry (when it has run out or is no longer wanted)
Notify users when an item's quantity is running low or expiration date is near
